{"tid":2420940,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國會媒體「Roll Call」報導 美中國專家：解放軍將領透露　習近平將於2年內拿下台灣","createTime":"2021-02-24T07:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T11:22:02.000Z","uid":204533,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ff096d392e3c10d55c88b53367bfd1083734a588","tid":2420940,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"中國不斷打壓台灣國際空間並威脅武統台灣。美國學者日前透露表示，中國國家主席習近平很可能計畫在1、2年內拿下台灣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">美國國會媒體「Roll Call」報導，美國中國專家近日向國會議員指出，隨著中國軍力不斷增強，美國協助台灣抵擋入侵的問題及能力愈加複雜和脆弱化。</span></strong>研究中國軍力的史丹佛大學學者梅惠琳（Oriana Skylar Mastro）本月18日在一場視訊會議上向美中經濟與安全評估委員會表示，美國協助台灣阻擋對岸侵襲的能力，<strong><span class=\"red\">「毫無疑問地已是韓戰以來最弱時期」。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n梅惠琳指出，過去北京的態度是，只要台灣正式宣布獨立，就會發動戰爭，但現在態度改變。她說：<strong><span class=\"red\">「我認為現在最大的威脅是，北京將以軍事行動強迫兩岸統一，不管華府和台北的政策或作法。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n梅惠琳還說，<strong><span class=\"red\">有解放軍將領向她表示，習近平認為軍方有能力在一兩年內拿下並佔領台灣。西方專家則分析認為，中國很可能在5年後才能達成武統台灣的目標。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n梅惠琳表示，<strong><span class=\"red\">習近平正在等待時機</span></strong>，若有美國高層外交官訪問台灣，或是繼續向台灣軍售，北京便可以此為藉口出兵。她說：「中國會在一切都準備好之後才採取行動，所以除非北京一切就緒，中共高層會謹慎考量所有美方和台灣的行動，只要這些行動不是為了獨立，他們會盡量避免開戰。」<br />\n<br />\n她和其他兩岸問題專家建議，拜登政府應該加強台灣與國際社會接軌，而美國也應靠其他盟國的力量，讓北京認知若侵犯台灣，恐導致各國聯手反制，「他們這樣才會知道，『國家偉大復興』的代價有多龐大」。（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"b4c856cf27e556845d9c03caa068de4822d9e6c6","tid":2420940,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210224/HAE3OL4XARA4ZPPP6BETQGP5RU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210224%2FHAE3OL4XARA4ZPPP6BETQGP5RU%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpmwxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=dc6ed0cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210224%2FHAE3OL4XARA4ZPPP6BETQGP5RU%2F&h=e1900f58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210224/HAE3OL4XARA4ZPPP6BETQGP5RU/</a>"},{"pid":"41a0954cea6f40e3514b871c0e4c83a0676e44f2","tid":2420940,"uid":375684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"又想問元老院攞錢買新玩具?"},{"pid":"8097cae2440fea13868633275a0c803f65df2e12","tid":2420940,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"左鳩: 如果弊燈上任後  中共攻打台灣  我會道歉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b1ab74e1a1596f4af3ac4f0f453c878c100a9d","tid":2420940,"uid":204533,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdc82ce2fcda81c094a41b02807272bd22edcf6","tid":2420940,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i0uF0sV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0uF0sV.gif&h=a91e0af7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67882a5a49eb5bd0ee8887e596861d5cdb2ca244","tid":2420940,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07b1ab74e1a1596f4af3ac4f0f453c878c100a9d","tid":2420940,"uid":204533,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"我諗香港人唔會低估佢既癲<br />\n係睇歐美班天真膠幾時醒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb319a09c7c0ecd639040bd24054152366521e2d","tid":2420940,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:59:46.000Z","msg":"真心希望打台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2edb08aff5c2fc8d5f5240a5429ede7ac95122f","tid":2420940,"uid":33868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:01:2